  "body": "See https://discordapp.com/channels/593655374469660673/593655641445367808/725848665327140917\r\n\r\nWe should save the ENR to disk whenever it updates.\r\nIt may be difficult to have ENR extend EventEmitter (as it currently already extends Map), but we may find another way to keep the ENR updated on disk.\r\nA strawman proposal:\r\nExtend ENR with a subclass which accepts a path in its constructor, overrides `set` to save to disk after updating.",
